<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Delta Scripts Hub</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #090314 0%, #170b2e 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0; padding: 0;
            display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .header-container { text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .logo-title { font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #8a2be2; margin: 10px 0; }
        .subscribers { color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        .button-container { width: 90%; max-width: 500px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 15px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .hado-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6c11d0 0%, #490ca0 100%);
            border: 1px solid #8e32ff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 18px 20px;
            color: white; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;
            display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(108, 17, 208, 0.3); transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .hado-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(142, 50, 255, 0.5); }
        .btn-action { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 5px 15px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 12px; }
        .section-title { width: 90%; max-width: 500px; text-align: right; font-size: 14px; color: #66fcf1; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding-bottom: 5px; text-shadow: 0 0 5px #66fcf1; }
        .script-box {
            width: 90%; max-width: 500px; background: #120724; border: 1px solid #2d134d; border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 20px; box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); margin-bottom: 25px; box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .script-title { color: #39ff14; margin-top: 0; font-size: 18px; text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(57,255,20,0.5); text-align: right; }
        .code-area { background-color: #050505; color: #39ff14; padding: 12px; border-radius: 6px; font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; direction: ltr; text-align: left; overflow-x: auto; border: 1px solid #333; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 10px; word-break: break-all; white-space: pre-wrap; }
        .footer { color: #555555; font-size: 12px; margin-top: auto; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class='header-container'>
    <div class='logo-title'>⚡ DELTA SCRIPTS HUB ⚡</div>
    <div class='subscribers'>أقوى وأحدث السكربتات المجانية</div>
  </div>

  <div class='button-container'>
    <a class='hado-btn' href='#' target='_blank'>
      <span>▶ Discord Server</span>
      <span class='btn-action'>JOIN</span>
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class='section-title'>POPULAR GAMES SCRIPTS</div>

  <!-- سكربت 1 -->
  <div class='script-box'>
    <div class='script-title'>🟢 1. سكربت بلوكس فروت (Blox Fruits)</div>
    <div class='code-area'>loadstring(game:HttpGet("https://githubusercontent.com"))()</div>
  </div>

  <!-- سكربت 2 -->
  <div class='script-box'>
    <div class='script-title'>🔴 2. سكربت بليد بول (Blade Ball)</div>
    <div class='code-area'>loadstring(game:HttpGet("https://githubusercontent.com"))()</div>
  </div>

  <div class='footer'>© 2026 Delta Scripts Hub</div>

</body>
</html>
